lead_paragraph: The SEAL member was the third American serviceman to die in combat since a United States-led coalition began battling the group in the country in 2014.

headline.print_headline: SEAL Team Member Dies Fighting ISIS in Iraq
headline.main: Navy SEAL Is Killed in Northern Iraq in Fight With ISIS

snippet: The SEAL member was the third American serviceman to die in combat since a United States-led coalition began battling the group in the country in 2014.
abstract: Islamic State fighters kill Navy SEAL Charlie Keating IV after breaking through Kurdish defenses in northern Iraq; attack, described as largest in months, is part of effort to prevent Iraqi military from retaking Mosul; Keating is third service member to die in combat since coalition offensive against Islamic State began in 2014.
